title: Number of births in Norway 2008 to 2018
summary: The chart at hand is a line chart where the x axis denotes Year and a y axis denotes Number of live births. In total the number of data points it has is 11.
Overall Number of live births has decreased over the Year.
The most drastic decrease took place within the Year 2016 and 2017.
Maximum Number of live births, about 61807.0 was reported at Year 2009
The lowest Number of live births, of value 55120.0 was reported at Year 2018
